      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/trader-joes-lawsuit-over-heavy-metals-chocolate-is-largely-dismissed-2024-03-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名美国法官驳回了大部分诉讼，指控 Trader Joe’s 未能披露其黑巧克力棒含有有害含量的“重金属”（如铅和镉），从而误导和危害消费者。]]></description>
